17
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:32,240
I didn't tell you because

18
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,719
he's still on probation.

19
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,520
Yeah, I just started

20
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,960
